<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Languages_of_the_European_Union&action=edit&section=1.php.html" title="Edit section: Official EU languages">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Official_EU_languages">Official EU languages</span></h2>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:172px;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:European_Parliament_languages.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b6/European_Parliament_languages.jpg/170px-European_Parliament_languages.jpg" width="170" height="227" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b6/European_Parliament_languages.jpg/255px-European_Parliament_languages.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b6/European_Parliament_languages.jpg/340px-European_Parliament_languages.jpg 2x" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:European_Parliament_languages.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="http://bits.wikimedia.org/static-1.21wmf9/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
Sign in the entrance of the <a href="European_Parliament" title="European Parliament">European Parliament</a> building in <a href="Brussels" title="Brussels">Brussels</a> written in all <a href="Official_language" title="Official language">official languages</a> used in the <a href="European_Union" title="European Union">European Union</a>.</div>
</div>
</div>
