<th scope="row" class="navbox-group" style=";;"><a href="History_of_the_European_Union" title="History of the European Union">History</a></th>
<td style="text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;background:transparent;;;background:transparent;" class="navbox-list navbox-odd">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em"></div>
<table cellspacing="0" class="nowraplinks navbox-subgroup" style="border-spacing:0;;;;">
<tr>
<th scope="row" class="navbox-group" style=";width:6.5em;padding-left:0.5em;padding-right:0.5em;font-weight:normal;;"><a href="Timeline_of_European_Union_history" title="Timeline of European Union history">Timeline</a></th>
<td style="text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-odd">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em">
<ul>
<li><a href="Ideas_of_European_unity_before_1945" title="Ideas of European unity before 1945">Pre-1945</a></li>
<li><a href="History_of_the_European_Communities_(1945%E2%80%931957)" title="History of the European Communities (1945–1957)" class="mw-redirect">1945–1957</a></li>
